0alcohol%20during%20the%20week%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20drinks%20while%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20my%20doctoral%20work%20often%20led%20to%20bad%20decisions%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20couple%20more%20drinks%2C%20which%20then%20led%20me%20to%20take%20the%20night%20off%2C%20thinking%20that%20I'd%20have%20time%20to%20do%20the%20work%20the%20next%20day.%20Drinking%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommon-ways-coping-habits-making-anxiety-stress-worse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoping%20mechanism%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20become%20a%20habit.%20Life%20was%20hard%2C%20and%20alcohol%20numbed%20the%20self-critical%20voices%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20avoid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-wont-help-you-sober-up-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealcohol%20and%20caffeine%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20week%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20time%20for%20artificial%20highs%20or%20lows.%20After%20a%20difficult%20month%20of%20stopping%20cold%20turkey%2C%20not%20drinking%20became%20a%20better%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20found%20small%20moments%20to%20prioritize%20physical%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20way%20I%20had%20time%20for%20the%20gym%2C%20but%20there%20were%20things%20I%20could%20do%20to%20stay%20healthy.%20I%20did%20what%20I%20called%20%26quot%3Bthree%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20a%20one-minute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffew-minutes-of-wall-sits-can-lower-your-blood-pressure-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewall-sit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20one-minute%20plank%2C%20and%20one%20minute%20of%20sit-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20day%20that%20you%20can't%20find%20three%20minutes%20for%20yourself.%20I%20read%20journal%20articles%20during%20the%20three%20minutes%2C%20which%20was%20one%20of%20my%20few%20successful%20multi-tasks.%3C%