0else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hammoud%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20city's%20residents.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20tell%20you%20exactly%20how%20the%20villages%20are%20shaped%20because%20we've%20driven%20those%20roads.%20We've%20shopped%20at%20those%20markets.%20We%20have%20phone%20calls%20with%20people%20there%20as%20frequently%20as%20we%20have%20phone%20calls%20with%20our%20family%20members%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Many%20shops%20and%20restaurants%20in%20Dearborn%20advertise%20in%20Arabic%20alongside%20English.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660db9dc3f923f7dab045b1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20shops%20and%20restaurants%20in%20Dearborn%20advertise%20in%20Arabic%20alongside%20English.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Metzger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20Arab%20American%20community%20is%20particularly%20concentrated%20in%20the%20Detroit%20area%2C%20with%20implications%20for%202024%20in%20a%20closely-watched%20swing%20state%2C%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20Arab%20American%20voters%20scattered%20in%20competitive%20states%20around%20the%20country.%20The%20Arab%20American%20Institute%20estimates%20that%20there%20are%20206%2C000%20such%20voters%20in%20Florida%2C%20134%2C000%20in%20Virginia%2C%20and%20126%2C000%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichigan%20is%20a%20bellwether%20for%20what%20will%20happen%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Zogby%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20institute.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20canary%20in%20the%20coal%20mine%20for%20other%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20key%20to%20the%20movement's%20ongoing%20success%20has%20been%20coalition-building%20with%20other%20communities%2C%20including%20African%20American%20voters%2C%20young%20voters%2C%20and%20progressive%20Jewish%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThirty-six%20times%20in%20the%20Torah%2C%20it%20s