3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df41cb90413ab8e1d762d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOrganizers%20with%20the%20Listen%20to%20Michigan%20campaign%20following%20election%20results%20during%20a%20watch%20party%20in%20Dearborn%2C%20Michigan%20on%20February%2027%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Kowalsky%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20Uncommitted%20campaign%20of%20the%2080s%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zogby.%20After%20founding%20the%20Arab%20American%20Institute%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20in%201985%2C%20he%20and%20others%20worked%20in%20the%20intervening%20decades%20to%20build%20up%20Arab%20American%20power.%20Much%20of%20that%20work%20included%20registering%20voters%20and%20raising%20political%20consciousness%20in%20places%20like%20Dearborn%2C%20where%20non-Arab%20mayors%20had%20at%20times%20sought%20to%20fearmonger%20about%20the%20growing%20Arab%20American%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20work%20also%20took%20place%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20post-9%2F11%20era%2C%20when%20Arabs%20and%20Muslims%20in%20the%20US%20faced%20discrimination%20and%20political%20marginalization%20after%20the%20September%2011%2C%202001%20terror%20attacks.%20That%20marginalization%20persists%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20lesser%20form%2C%20to%20this%20day%3B%20in%20February%2C%20a%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20opinion%20writer%20described%20Dearborn%20as%20%26quot%3BAmerica's%20Jihad%20Capital%2C%26quot%3B%20prompting%20Mayor%20Hammoud%20to%20announce%20increased%20security%20measures%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20of%20organizing%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20what's%20emerged%20today%20%E2%80%94%20a%20voting%20bloc%20that%20not%20only%20poses%20a%20possible%20threat%20to%20Biden's%20reelection%2C%20but%20that%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20rejected%20what%20leaders%20view%20as%20political%20pandering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20while%20organizers%20have%20been%20clear%20that%20they're%20seeking%20specific%20policy%20changes%20from%20Biden%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20perception%20that%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-young-black-latino-voters-swing-states-democratic-party-trump-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreasingly%20nervous%3C%2Fa%3E%20presidential%20campaign%20has%20merely%20been%20making%20a%20play%20for%20votes.%20And%20there%20have%20been%20prominent%20missteps%20by%20Biden's%20administration%20and%20campaign%2C%20including%20a%20White%20House%20statement%20marking%20100%20days%20since%20October%207%20that%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20who%20had%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20even%20amid%20those%20missteps%20%E2%80%94%20interpreted%20often%20as%20disrespect%20%E2%80%93%20there's%20a%20sense%20of%20empowerment%20that%20comes%20with%20holding%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20election%20in%20your%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20understand%20that%20the%20Michigan%20Muslim%20and%20Arab%20community%20is%20large%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hammoud%2C%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%20not%20to%20elect%20a%20president%2C%20but%20maybe%20to%20make%20one%20lose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farab-americans-uncommitted-michigan-dearborn-biden-israel-gaza-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713013022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660c285c1caec1275a6be0fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farab-americans-uncommitted-michigan-dearborn-biden-israel-gaza-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bmetzger%40insider.com%20(Bryan%20Metzger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farab-americans-uncommitted-michigan-dearborn-biden-israel-gaza-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22am