Fa%3E%20critiised%20Chandrakant%20by%20terming%20his%20coaching%20style%20as%20%26quot%3Bmilitant%26quot%3B.%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20was%20the%20mentor%20of%20LSG%20during%20IPL%202021%20and%202022%2C%20joined%20KKR%20this%20season%20in%20the%20same%20role.%20Talking%20about%20the%20brief%20period%20of%20time%20he%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20celebrated%20coach%20of%20Indian%20domestic%20circuit%2C%20Gambhir%20said%20that%20he%20has%20not%20heard%20any%20criticism%20about%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Chandrakant's%20coaching%20Mumbai%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20enjoyed%20much%20success%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20And%20since%202023%20season%2C%20he%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20KKR%20as%20the%20coach%20of%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20certain%20issues%20going%20on%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20the%20team.%20Guys%20weren't%20happy%20with%20certain%20things%20that%20were%20going%20on%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20times%2C%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20changing%20room.%20There%20was%20a%20new%20coach%20coming%20in%20and%20he%20liked%20to%20do%20things%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20and%20that%20didn't%20sit%20well%20with%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Wiese%20had%20said%20'Hitman%20for%20Hire%3A%20A%20year%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20franchise%20cricketer'%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%20were%20frustrated%20because%20a%20lot%20changed%2C%20and%20the%20coach%20brought%20in%20things%20that%20he%20thought%20would%20bring%20success.%20But%20as%20an%20overseas%20player%2C%20they%20sometimes%20don't%20sit%20well.%20He's%20known%20in%20India%20as%20a%20fairly%20militant%20type%20of%20coach%2C%20a%20strict%20disciplinarian.%20The%20overseas%20guys%20who've%20played%20all%20over%20the%20world%20don't%20need%20someone%20coming%20in%20and%20telling%20him%20how%20to%20behave%20and%20what%20to%20wear%20and%20what%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20chill%20with%20it%2C%20but%20there%20were%20players%20more%20stubborn%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20experience%20of%20Gambhir%20with%20Chandrakant%20is%20definitely%20a%20different%20one%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20not%20heard%20about%20any%20criticism.%20It's%20been%20early%20days%2C%20and%20my%20working%20relationship%20with%20him%20has%20been%20really%20very%20good.%20Hopefully%2C%20it%20will%20continue%20that%20way.%20Whatever%20has%20been%20said%2C%20I%20have%20no%20clue%20about%20it.%20I%20think%20he%20has%20been%20pretty%20successful%20in%20first-class%20cricket%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20he%20has%20got%20this%20opportunity.%20So%20far%2C%20it%20has%20been%20really%20good%20working%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir%20as%20quoted%20by%20Times%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20KKR's%20star%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andre%20Russell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1536-andre-russell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndre%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20also%20backed%20the%20coach%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20been%20doing%20an%20amazing%20job'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713012900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8cf78c48_chandrakant-pandit-gautam-gambhir-x_625x300_13_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fon-kkrs-militant-coach-who-frustrated-players-in-ipl-2023-gautam-gambhir-says-this-5434079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20relationship%20with%20team's%20head%20coach%20Chandrakant%20Pandit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Malayalam%20film%20will%20be%20given%20to%20PVR-owned%20screen%20or%20theatre%3A%20FEFKA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713012814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2