and%20her%20husband%20on%20the%20Dominican%20Daze%20cruise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619204a3f923f7dab072e9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeft%3A%20Virgin%20Voyages%20Scarlet%20Lady%2C%20right%3A%20Eliza%20Green%20and%20her%20husband%20on%20the%20Dominican%20Daze%20cruise.%3Cp%3ELeft%3A%20Rachel%20Hosie%2FBusiness%20Insider%2C%20Right%3A%20Eliza%20Green%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMillennial%20Eliza%20Green%20avoided%20cruises%20because%20she%20felt%20they%20were%20germ-riddled%20and%20full%20of%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20friend%20suggested%20a%20surprise%20cruise%20on%20Virgin's%20child-free%20ship%20and%20Green%20apprehensively%20agreed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20loved%20the%20ship%20experience%20with%20sizeable%20rooms%20and%20fun%20activities%2C%20but%20the%20pace%20of%20travel%20was%20too%20quick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20millennial%20Eliza%20Green%2C%20who%20took%20her%20first%20cruise%20vacation%20on%20Virgin%20Voyages.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20thought%20cruise%20ships%20were%20a%20place%20to%20pick%20up%20germs%20from%20people%2C%20especially%20children.%20I'd%20heard%20nightmare%20stories%20of%20people%20getting%20sick%2C%20overcrowding%2C%20and%20bad%20food.%20But%20when%20friends%20approached%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20to%20go%20for%20a%2040th%20birthday%2C%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20frequent%20cruise%20traveler%20friend%20gave%20us%20a%20couple%20of%20options.%20Virgin%20Voyages%20sounded%20particularly%20appealing.%20The%20rooms%20were%20affordable%2C%20with%20balconies%20and%20no%20children.%20Plus%2C%20the%20five-night%20length%20felt%20manageable%20as%20a%20first-time%20cruiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20two%20other%20couples%2C%20and%20I%20embarked%20on%20Virgin%20Voyage's%20Scarlet%20Lady%20Dominican%20Daze.%20We%20set%20off%20from%20the%20port%20in%20Miami%20for%20two%20stops%20in%20Puerto%20Plata%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20and%20Bimini%2C%20Bahamas.%20For%20lodging%20and%20food%20for%20two%2C%20it%20cost%20%243%2C234.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%20skeptical%2C%20I%20went%20in%20with%20little%20expectations%20and%20just%20the%20hope%20of%20having%20a%20good%20time%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECruise%20food%20was%20better%20than%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20was%20a%20pleasant%20surprise%2C%20far%20better%20than%20the%20buffet%20options%20I'd%20imagined%20on%20other%20cruises.%20This%20was%20our%20first%20cruise%2C%20but%20it%20was%20our%20second%20all-inclusive-style%20vacation.%20Compared%20to%20the%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Jamaica%2C%20the%20cruise%20had%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20cuisines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20ship%20that%20had%20to%20serve%20thousands%2C%20the%20level%20of%20food%20and%20choices%20exceeded%20my%20expectations.%20I%20never%20ate%20the%20same%20meal%20twice.%20The%20ease%20of%20dining%20was%20seamless.%20Food%20was%20included%20in%20our%20prepaid%20rate%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20take%20out%20our%20wallets%20during%20mealtime%20or%20show%20our%20cruise%20wristband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20sit-down%20restaurants%2C%20grab-and-go%20stations%2C%20and%20dining%20hall-style%20venues.%20We%20made%20reservations%20before%20our%20trip%20since%20we%20had%20a%20large%20group%20and%20the%20tables%20booked%20up%20quickly.%20However%2C%20you%20could%20walk%20into%20restaurants%20or%20book%20upon%20embarking%20on%20the%20ship%20through%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20premium%20items%20for%20an%20extra%20cost%2C%20such%20as%20lobster%20or%20wagyu%2C%20but%20they%20were%20unneeded%20because%20there%20was%20already%20so%20much%20food%20provided.%20Although%20alcohol%20was%20an%20extra%20cost%2C%20the%20prepaid%20option%20gave%20us%20extra%20dollars%20toward%20drinks%2C%20which%20was%20a%20good%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20cabin%20was%20a%20needed%20respite%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20traveling%20on%20a%20cruise%2C%20I'd%20heard%20of%20windowless%20cabins%20and%20cramped%20rooms.%20Throughout%20the%20journey%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20spending%20time%20in%20my%20room%2C%20which%20I%20hadn't%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20concerned%20about%20seasickness%20in%20a%20confined%20space%20on%20the%20water.%20I%20came%20prepared%20with%20motion%20sickness%20remedies%2C%20but%20it%20never%20hit%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20room%20was%20sizable%20and%20nicer%20than%20many%20hotel%20rooms%20I%20have%20stayed%20in%20on%20land.%20The%20cabin%20felt%20huge%20compared%20to%20the%20hotel%20I'd%20stayed%20at%20in%20Miami%20before%20embarking%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20bed%2C%20seating%2C%20and%20ample%20closet%20space%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20decent%20bathroom.%20I%20never%20felt%20cramped%20or%20like%20I%20was%20stumbling%20around%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20somewhat%20of%20an%20introvert%2C%20the%20room%20was%20a%20nice%20respite.%20When%20I%20wanted%20time%20to%20recharge%2C%20the%20hammock%20on%20the%20balcony%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20read%20and%20gave%20me%20an%20escape%2C%20making%20the%20trip%20more%20relaxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20entertainment%20wasn't%20cheesy%20like%20I%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hadn't%20planned%20to%20partake%20in%20much%20of%20the%20entertainment%20because%20I%20assumed%20it%20would%20be%20cheesy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20the%20shows%20and%20activities%20defied%20my%20expectations.%20We%20enjoyed%20a%20puzzle%20contest%20one%20night%2C%20and%20another%20night%2C%20when%20we%20stumbled%20upon%20an%20entertainment%20show%3B%20the%20performance%20was%20impressive%20and%20well-produced%20with%20polished%20performers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirgin%20did%20a%20nice%20job%20of%20giving%20every%20traveler%20their%20own%20experience%20despite%20being%20on%20the%20same%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boat's%20layout%20made%20it%20so%20we%20didn't%20hear%20noise%20from%20the%20louder%20late-night%20parties%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20detract%20from%20our%20vacation.%20I%20liked%20being%20able%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20our%20friends%20on%20the%20cruise%20and%20also%20seek%20out%20our%20own%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHigh-tech%20amenities%20meant%20the%20service%20was%20great%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20offerings%20were%20shared%20in%20an%20app%2C%20which%20we%20could%20easily%20access%20onboard%20from%20our%20phones.%20The%20well-thought-out%20amenities%2C%20such%20as%20using%20a%20wristband%20for%20drinks%20and%20not%20having%20to%20show%20a%20room%20card%20for%20dinner%2C%20made%20it%20so%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20think%20about%20anything.%20We%20truly%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bartending%20staff%20was%20friendly%2C%20and%20the%20service%20was%20impressive.%20Plus%2C%20the%20layout%20of%20the%20boat%20was%20easy%20to%20navigate.%20We%20took%20advantage%20of%20the%20laundry%20service%20for%20a%20small%20fee%2C%20as%20it%20was%20reasonable%20and%20made%20our%20trip%20more%20convenient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20boat%20offered%20other%20amenities%2C%20such%20as%20a%20gym%2C%20gaming%20areas%2C%20spa%2C%20and%20shopping%20boutiques.%20They%20even%20had%20a%20tattoo%20parlor%20onboard%20and%20a%20medical-grade%20spa%20offering%20botox.%20Even%20though%20we%20didn't%20end%20up%20using%20these%20additional%20services%2C%20it%20was%20still%20nice%20to%20know%20they%20were%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20could%20have%20spent%20longer%20at%20the%20destinations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20destinations%20were%20the%20most%20disappointing%20part%20of%20our%20experience.%20The%20cruise%20made%20a%20stop%20in%20Puerto%20Plata%20and%20Bimini.%20Since%20they%20were%20around%20six%20hours%20each%2C%20including%20disembarking%20and%20embarking%2C%20we%20didn't%20get%20to%20experience%20as%20much%20of%20the%20culture%20as%20we%20would%20have%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20a%20pre-booked%20waterfall%20excursion%20in%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%2C%20which%20we%20paid%20for%20separately.%20Bimini%20felt%20like%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20cruise%20because%20we%20stopped%20at%20a%20Virgin-owned%20beach%20club%20for%20the%20day.%20It%20was%20fun%2C%20but%20we%20wish%20we%20could%20have%20seen%20more%20of%20the%20island%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20despite%20that%2C%20we%20felt%20the%20cruise%20was%20a%20good%20value.%20The%20quality%20of%20the%20food%20and%20the%20room%20alone%20made%20it%20worth%20the%20investment.%20Plus%2C%20the%20boat%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20travel%20with%20friends.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20we%20would%20cruise%20again%2C%20especially%20if%20we%20could%20have%20more%20time%20at%20each%20stop%20to%20improve%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-skeptical-loved-first-cruise-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713011522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619204a3f923f7dab072e9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-skeptical-loved-first-cruise-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20skeptical%20millennial%20thought%20cruises%20were%20full%20of%20germs%20and%20kids.%20But%20her%20first%20cruise%20experience%20exceeded%20her%20expectations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sophie%20Katzman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-skeptical-loved-first-cruise-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It's%20not%20just%20gold.%20Commodities%20from%20copper%20to%20cocoa%20are%20seeing%20huge%20gains%20in%202024.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gold%20nugget%20miner%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66194cd11caec1275a6f883d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small-scale%20miner%20holds%20his%20gold%20that%20was%20melted%20together%20at%20a%20processing%20plant%20located%20around%20100km%20(62%20miles)%20north%20of%20the%20Mongolian%20capital%20city%20Ulan%20Bator%20April%205%2C%202012.%20%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FDavid%20Gray%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGold%2C%20copper%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20cocoa%20are%20up%20big%20as%20a%20broad%20takes%20hold%20in%20the%20commodities%20sector.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rally%20is%20driving%20historic%20profits%20for%20the%20commodities%20trading%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaterial%20shortages%20and%20macro%20uncertainty%20are%20key%20reasons%20why%20commodities%20are%20climbing%2C%20traders%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20that%20glitters%20is%20gold%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20because%20other%20raw%20materials%20are%20shining%20just%20as%20bright.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommodity%20trading%20has%20been%20booming%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20Apex%20Trader%20Funding%20CEO%20Darrell%20Martin%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20as%20everything%20from%20industrial%20metals%20to%20oil%20runs%20hotter%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20volatility%20created%20by%20these%20big%20moves%20creates%20a%20ton%20of%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20creating%20a%20lot%20of%20volatility%20intraday%2C%20which%20is%20amazing%20for%20traders.%20It's%20giving%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20opportunities%20to%20go%20in%20and%20to%20produce%20income%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPropping%20up%20the%20rally%20is%20big%20upside%20among%20a%20plethora%20of%20physica