0cocoa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20copper%20supply%20crisis%20is%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America%20titled%20a%20Monday%20note%3A%20%26quot%3BTight%20copper%20mine%20supply%20is%20increasingly%20constraining%20refined%20production%3A%20the%20much-discussed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcopper-prices-could-soar-33-in-the-next-year-as-global-inventories-hit-lowest-since%2F2e3c17j%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elack%20of%20mine%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20finally%20starting%20to%20bite.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metal%20is%20estimated%20to%20hit%20%245.44%20a%20pound%20by%202026%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20representing%2027%25%20upside%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcommodity.com%2Fprecious-metals%2Fcopper%2Fprice%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DToday%2527s%2520copper%2520market%2520price%2520is%2Cprices%2520like%2520gold%2520and%2520silver.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20price%20of%20%244.28%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20pound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20this%20year%2C%20it's%20climbed%2011.6%25%2C%20a%20boom%20that%20both%20Currie%20and%20Martin%20associated%20with%20a%20post-pandemic%20production%20rebound.%20But%20in%20Bank%20of%20America's%20view%2C%20copper%20is%20also%20the%20epicenter%20of%20the%20energy%20transition%2C%20and%20will%20further%20benefit%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20data%20centers%20expand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20similar%20story%20for%20cocoa%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcocoa-prices-bitcoin-rally-commodity-markets-investors-trading-finance-chocolate-2024-3%5C%22%3Edroughts%20and%20bad%20harvests%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20rocketed%20the%20ingredient%20to%20records.%20Over%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20cocoa%20futures%20have%20gained%20256%25%2C%20and%20a%20metric%20ton%20costs%20a%20record%20%2410%2C900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20may%20seem%20