0air%20war%20and%20the%20significant%20increase%20in%20available%20targets%20provided%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-ai-system-wheres-daddy-strikes-hamas-family-homes-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20always%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20better%20or%20for%20worse.%20With%20every%20use%2C%20these%20programs%20gain%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20that%20they%20then%20employ%20in%20future%20decision-making.%20With%20an%20accuracy%20rate%20of%2090%25%2C%20as%20the%20reporting%20indicates%2C%20Lavender's%20machine%20learning%20could%20be%20reinforcing%20both%20its%20correct%20and%20incorrect%20kills%2C%20Ryan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELetting%20AI%20do%20the%20decision-making%20in%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-of-warfare-is-catastrophic-and-robotic-former-general-says-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFuture%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20see%20AI%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20humans%20to%20process%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20and%20suggest%20potential%20courses%20of%20action%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20battle.%20But%20there%20are%20several%20possibilities%20that%20could%20taint%20such%20a%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gathered%20data%20could%20be%20too%20much%20for%20humans%20to%20process%20or%20understand.%20If%20an%20AI%20program%20is%20processing%20massive%20amounts%20of%20information%20to%20make%20a%20list%20of%20possible%20targets%2C%20it%20could%20reach%20a%20point%20where%20humans%20are%20quickly%20overwhelmed%20and%20unable%20to%20meaningfully%20contribute%20to%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20moving%20too%20quickly%20and%20making%20assumptions%20based%20on%20the%20data%2C%20which%20increases%20the%20likelihood%20that%20mistakes%20are%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20inspect%20damage%20and%20remove%20items%20from%20their%20homes%20following%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20on%20April%2007%2C%202024%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20Gaza.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66198d3d1caec1275a6fbe26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20inspect%20damage%20and%20remove%20items%20from%20their%20homes%20following%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20on%20April%2007%2C%202024%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%2C%20Gaza.%3Cp%3EAhmad%20Hasaballah%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInternational%20Committee%20Red%20Cross%20Military%20and%20Armed%20Group%20Adviser%20Ruben%20Stewart%20and%20Legal%20Adviser%20Georgia%20Hinds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.icrc.org%2Flaw-and-policy%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Falgorithms-of-war-use-of-artificial-intelligence-decision-making-armed-conflict%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20a%20problem%20back%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20touted%20military%20advantage%20of%20AI%20is%20the%20increase%20in%20tempo%20of%20decision-making%20it%20would%20give%20a%20user%20over%20their%20adversary.%20Increased%20tempo%20often%20creates%20additional%20risks%20to%20civilians%2C%20which%20is%20why%20techniques%20that%20reduce%20the%20tempo%2C%20such%20as%20'tactical%20patience%2C'%20are%20employed%20to%20reduce%20civilian%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20quest%20to%20move%20quickly%2C%20humans%20could%20take%20their%20hands%20off%20the%20wheel%2C%20trusting%20the%20AI%20with%20little%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%2B972%20Magazine%20and%20Local%20Call%20report%2C%20AI-picked%20targets%20were%20only%20reviewed%20for%20about%2020%20seconds%2C%20typically%20just%20to%20ensure%20the%20potential%20kill%20was%20male%2C%20before%20a%20strike%20was%20authorized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20reporting%20raises%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloud.prio.org%2Ffiles%2F13c020fb-0047-4fc7-a44f-075374b07f2c%2FCole%2520et%2520al%2520-%2520Artificial%2520Intelligence%2520in%2520Military%2520Planning%2520and%2520Operations%2520PRIO%2520Paper%25202024.pdf%3Finline%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserious%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20to%20what%20extent%20a%20human%20being%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20loop%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20decision-making%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprocess.%20According%20to%20Singer%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20potential%20%26quot%3Billustration%20of%20what%20is%20sometimes%20known%20as%20'automation%20bias%2C'%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20a%20situation%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20human%20deludes%20themselves%20into%20thinking%20that%20because%20the%20machine%20provided%20the%20answer%2C%20it%20must%20be%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20while%20a%20human%20is%20'in%20the%20loop%2C'%20they%20aren't%20doing%20the%20job%20that%20is%20assumed%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Singer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20October%2C%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20and%20the%20President%20of%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20Mirjana%20Spoljaric%2C%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2023%2Fsg2264.doc.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20joint%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20militaries%20%26quot%3Bmust%20act%20now%20to%20preserve%20human%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20force%26quot%3B%20in%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuman%20control%20must%20be%20retained%20in%20life%20and%20death%20decisions.%20The%20autonomous%20targeting%20of%20humans%20by%20machines%20is%20a%20moral%20line%20that%20we%20must%20not%20cross%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BMachines%20with%20the%20power%20and%20discretion%20to%20take%20lives%20without%20human%20involvement%20should%20be%20prohibited%20by%20international%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width