Court%20overturning%20Roe%20v.%20Wade.%20The%20former%20president%20has%20repeatedly%20bragged%20about%20his%20role%20in%20appointing%20the%20three%20justices%20that%20provided%20the%20necessary%20margin%20for%20the%20high%20court%20to%20issue%20its%20landmark%20ruling%20in%20Dobbs%20v.%20Jackson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETrump%20has%20unsuccessfully%20tried%20to%20pivot%20away%20from%20abortion.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20of%20course%2C%20had%20no%20say%20in%20appointing%20any%20of%20the%20seven%20Arizona%20Supreme%20Court%20justices.%20All%20seven%2C%20including%20the%20one%20justice%20who%20recused%20himself%20from%20the%20case%20after%20his%20Facebook%20Post%20calling%20abortion%20%26quot%3Bthe%20greatest%20genocide%20known%20to%20man%26quot%3B%20resurfaced%2C%20were%20appointed%20by%20GOP%20governors.%20On%20Friday%2C%20before%20Harris'%20rally%2C%20Trump%20publicly%20pleaded%20for%20the%20Arizona%20legislature%20to%20repeal%20the%201864%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20Arizona%20went%20too%20far%20on%20their%20Abortion%20Ruling%2C%20enacting%20and%20approving%20an%20inappropriate%20Law%20from%201864%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social.%20%26quot%3BSo%20now%20the%20Governor%20and%20the%20Arizona%20Legislature%20must%20use%20HEART%2C%20COMMON%20SENSE%2C%20and%20ACT%20IMMEDIATELY%2C%20to%20remedy%20what%20has%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20Arizona%20ruling%2C%20the%20former%20president%20tried%20to%20wash%20his%20hands%20of%20the%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20that%20the%20future%20of%20abortion%20rights%20should%20be%20determined%20at%20the%20state%20level%20either%20by%20legislation%2C%20at%20the%20ballot%20box%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20both.%20His%20declaration%20left%20many%20questions%20unanswered%2C%20particularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-abortion-stance-timeline-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiven%20his%20shifting%20vi