2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Finfected-belly-button-piercing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebelly%20button%20piercings%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20moving%20from%20fringe%20to%20pop.%20I%20saw%20piercing%20studios%20as%20a%20means%20to%20an%20end%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20belly%20button%20and%20nose%20pierced.%20It%20was%20a%20different%20world%20I%20briefly%20inhabited.%20A%20world%20still%20a%20bit%20edgy%20and%20definitely%20more%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20a%20place%20I%20go%20on%20a%20Monday%20night%20to%20get%20my%20daughter's%20ears%20pierced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-piercer-kids-ear-piercings-safety-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713008642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66184b453f923f7dab0718a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-piercer-kids-ear-piercings-safety-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Piercing%20guns%20can't%20be%20sterilized.%20When%20my%20kindergartener%20asked%20for%20her%20ears%20pierced%2C%20I%20took%20her%20to%20a%20professional%20piercer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Saba%20Khonsari)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-piercer-kids-ear-piercings-safety-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20lodges%20graft%20case%20against%20Megha%20Engg%2C%20steel%20ministry%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713008529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109271458%2Cimgsize-719394.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcbi-books-megha-engineering-8-steel-ministry-officials-in-rs-315-crore-corruption-case%2Farticleshow%2F109271307.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20Megha%20Engineering%20and%20Infrastructure%20Ltd%20and%20eight%20officials%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Steel%20for%20an%20alleged%20corruption%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20315%20crores%20in%20the%20NISP%20project%20execution.%20The%20accused%20officers%20belong%20to%20the%20NMDC%20Iron%20and%20Steel%20Plant.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20also%20charged%20two%20officials%20of%20MECON%20for%20reportedly%20accepting%20a%20bribe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcbi-books-megha-engineering-8-steel-ministry-officials-in-rs-315-crore-corruption-case%2Farticleshow%2F109271307.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sugar%20Left%20A%20Sour%20Taste%3F%20Why%20Bournvita%20Lost%20'Health%20Drink'%20Tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20year%20after%20an%20influencer%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20high%20sugar%20content%20in%20Bournvita%20and%20four%20months%20since%20it%20was%20reduced%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20asked%20e-commerce%20companies%20to%20remove%20the%20brand%20and%20all%20other%20drinks%20and%20beverages%20from%20the%20'health%20drink'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20advisory%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20term%20'health%20drink'%20is%20not%20defined%20under%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20(FSS)%20Act%202006%20or%20rules%20submitted%20by%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Authority%20of%20India%20(FSSAI)%20and%20Mondelez%20-%20which%20owns%20Bournvita%2C%20Cadbury%20and%20several%20other%20large%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNational%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%2C%20a%20statutory%20body%20constituted%20under%20Section%20(3)%20of%20the%20Commission%20of%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(CPCR)%20Act%2C%202005%2C%20after%20its%20inquiry%20under%20Section%2014%20of%20CRPC%20Act%202005%20concluded%20that%20there%20is%20no%20'health%20drink'%20defined%20under%20FSS%20Act%202006%2C%20rules%20and%20regulations%20submitted%20by%20FSSAI%20and%20Mondelez%20India%20Food%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20IANS%20quoted%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20ministry%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20NCPCR%20had%20asked%20Bournvita%20to%20withdraw%20all%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20advertisements%2C%20packaging%20and%20labels%20soon%20after%20a%20video%20by%20influencer%20Revant%20Himatsingka%2C%20aka%20FoodPharmer%2C%20highlighting%20the%20drink's%20high%20sugar%20content%20went%20viral%20and%20sparked%20widespread%20criticism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Himatsingka%20had%20accused%20Cadbury%20of%20making%20false%20claims%20about%20the%20health%20benefits%20of%20Bournvita%20and%20%26quot%3Bmiscommunicating%26quot%3B%20its%20%26quot%3Bnutritional%20value%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%2050%20grams%20of%20sugar%20per%20100%20grams.%20Basically%2C%20the%20entire%20half%20of%20this%20bag%20is%20only%20sugar%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20months%20later%2C%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Mondelez%20said%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwatch-bournvita-reduces-added-sugar-by-14-4-after-criticism-influencer-calls-it-big-win-4733774%5C%22%3Ehad%20reduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20by%2014.4%25%20-%20from%2037.4%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%20per%20100%20grams%20to%2032.2%20grams%20per%20100%20grams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fif-you-send-legal-notice-ill-get-you-noticed-influencer-on-bournvita-win-4751679%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Mondelez's%20announcement%2C%20the%20influencer%20had%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20a%20major%20win%20for%20nutritional%20education%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20win.%20I%20know%2015%25%20may%20not%20sound%20like%20much%20(of%20a%20reduction)%2C%20but%20for%20a%20multinational%20corporation%20to%20do%20this%20is%20pretty%20staggering.%20I%20hope%20this%20leads%20to%20a%20chain%20reaction%2C%20and%20other%20companies%20follow%20suit%20and%20try%20to%20improve%20their%20products.%20Lakhs%20of%20parents%20are%20now%20reading%20labels%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20people%20are%20eating%20slightly%20more%20consciously%2C%20so%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20win%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry's%20notification%20on%20Wednesday%20followed%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20NCPCR%20which%20found%20that%20the%20sugar%20levels%20in%20Bournvita%20were%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20acceptable%20limits.%20The%20child%20rights%20body%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20FSSAI%20to%20act%20against%20companies%20labelling%20supplements%20'health%20drinks'%20and%20failing%20to%20meet%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20has%20said%20that%20'health%20drink'%20has%20not%20been%20defined%20under%20the%20FSS%20Act%20and%20labelling%20any%20beverage%20that%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20rules.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Below%20Recommended%20Sugar%20Limit'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20is%20well%20below%20the%20recommended%20daily%20sugar%20limit%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20earlier%20statement%2C%20the%20company%20had%20said%2C%C2%A0Bournvita%20has%20enjoyed%20the%20love%20and%20trust%20of%20consumers%20for%20over%20seven%20decades.%20Bournvita%20contains%20nutrients%20namely%20Vitamin%20A%2C%20C%2C%20D%2C%20Iron%2C%20Zinc%2C%20Copper%20and%20Selenium%20which%20help%20build%20immunity.%20These%20have%20been%20part%20of%20our%20formulation%20for%20several%20years.%20We%20have%20always%20called%20out%20'Helps%20with%20healthy%20functioning%20of%20the%20immune%20system'%20on%20the%20back%20of%20our%20pack%20for%20several%20years%20(even%20before%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20serve%20of%20Bournvita%20has%207.5%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%2C%20which%20is%20approximately%20one%20and%20a%20half%20teaspoons.%20This%20is%20much%20less%20than%20the%20daily%20recommended%20intake%20limits%20of%20sugar%20for%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713008520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flcc970h_bournvita_625x300_13_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugar-left-a-sour-taste-why-bournvita-lost-health-drink-tag-5433693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%20a%20year%20after%20an%20influencer%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20high%20sugar%20content%20in%20Bournvita%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20asked%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20the%20brand%20and%20all%20other%20drinks%20and%20beverages%20from%20the%20'health%20drink'%20category.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugar-left-a-sour-taste-why-bournvita-lost-health-drink-tag-5433693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugar-left-a-sour-taste-why-bournvita-lost-health-drink-tag-5433693%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsugar-left-a-sour-taste-why-bournvita-lost-health-drink-tag-5433693%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Sushma%20Swaraj's%20Daughter%20Bansuri%20Said%20On%20Dynasty%20Politics%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20daughter%20of%20late%20Union%20minister%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20said%20the%20values%20of%20Sangh%20run%20through%20her%20veins%20and%20that%20she%20cannot%20even%20think%20of%20filling%20her%20mother's%20shoes%20owing%20to%20her%20stature%20and%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20PTI%20editors%20at%20the%20agency's%20headquarters%2C%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20reminisced%20the%20deep%20connection%20she%20had%20with%20her%20mother%20since%20childhood%20and%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20continued%20the%20late%20minister's%20tradition%20of%20sending%20BJP%20veteran%20L%20K%20Advani%20his%20favourite%20cake%20on%20his%20birthday%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20only%20child%20of%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20and%20Swaraj%20Kaushal%2C%20said%20while%20growing%20up%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strict%20rule%20in%20the%20house%20--%20she%20had%20to%20converse%20with%20her%20mother%20in%20Hindi%2C%20and%20father%20in%20English%20--%20which%20made%20her%20proficient%20in%20both%20the%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-year-old%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%2C%20the%20youngest%20BJP%20candidate%20in%20Delhi%2C%20said%20she%20had%20a%20normal%20upbringing%20which%20has%20kept%20her%20grounded%20while%20her%20family%20consisting%20of%20her%20parents%20and%20grandparents%20had%20a%20nationalistic%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20humbly%20submit%20that%20I%20am%20in%20politics%20not%20because%20of%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20and%20I%20say%20this%20with%20great%20responsibility.%20My%20'Sangh%20Ayu'%20(affiliation)%20is%2024%20years.%20I%20started%20my%20political%20life%20as%20an%20ABVP%20worker%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20served%20the%20party%20and%20organisation%20as%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20I%20got%20the%20first%20responsibility%20in%20the%20party%20as%20co-convener%20of%20the%20legal%20cell%20of%20Delhi%20BJP%2C%20four%20years%20after%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20my%20mother%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20dynasty%20politics%20is%20concerned%2C%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20said%20she%20deserves%20the%20same%20opportunities%20as%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitics%20should%20not%20be%20forbidden%20for%20me%20just%20because%20my%20mother%20was%20a%20public%20representative%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20have%20been%20dynasty%20politics%20had%20I%20owned%20the%20party%20and%20become%20its%20head%20and%20a%20top%20contender%20just%20after%20joining.%20But%20the%20equality%20of%20opportunity%20is%20justified%20for%20all%20whether%20it's%20Sushma%20Swaraj's%20daughter%20or%20anyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20said%20her%20parents%20invested%20much%20of%20their%20time%20in%20her%20to%20ensure%20that%20she%20achieved%20her%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learnt%20everything%20from%20my%20mom%20and%20dad.%20When%20you%20are%20the%20only%20child%2C%20you%20become%20a%20project%20for%20your%20parents.%20They%20really%20want%20to%20invest%20themselves%20in%20you.%20I%20think%20they%20really%20give%20their%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20pressure%26quot%3B%20on%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20aspect%20of%20her%20stature%20and%20legacy%2C%20I%20think%20is%20something%20that%20weighs%20on%20other%20peoples'%20minds.%20I%20am%20not%20even%20trying%20to%20be%20her%20imitation%20as%20that%20would%20be%20the%20greatest%20disservice%20to%20her%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20invested%20so%20much%20in%20me%20not%20so%20that%20I%20become%20a%20copy%20of%20her.%20She%20wanted%20me%20to%20be%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20a%20fool%20to%20try%20to%20fill%20her%20shoes.%20There%20can%20only%20be%20one%20Sushma%20Swaraj.%20However%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it%20is%20my%20endeavour%20not%20to%20do%20anything%20that%20hurts%20her%20repute%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBansuri%20recalled%20how%20her%20mother%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20accompany%20her%20to%20the%20pick-up%20point%20of%20the%20school%20bus%20every%20morning%20and%20be%20present%20at%20the%20drop-off%20point%20every%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20an%20amazing%20mom%2C%20really%20amazing.%20She%20was%20there%20at%20all%20annual%20day%20events%20of%20the%20school%20-%20even%20when%20I%20played%20an%20orange%20or%20a%20tree%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushma%20Swaraj%2C%20a%20BJP%20stalwart%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Minister%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20was%20a%20popular%20leader%20with%20a%20distinct%20style%20of%20speech%20that%20endeared%20her%20to%20party%20workers%20and%20supporters.%20She%20died%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20story%20behind%20her%20name%2C%20she%20said%20her%20mother%20was%20a%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20and%20used%20to%20say%20that%20a%20'bansuri'%20or%20a%20flute%20was%20%26quot%3Bdearest%26quot%3B%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBansuri%20was%20always%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20Radha%20rani%20or%20Lord%20Krishna%20himself%2C%20she%20used%20to%20say.%20My%20father%20wanted%20me%20to%20be%20named%20after%20some%20musical%20instrument.%20So%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20name%20me%20Bansuri%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20mother%20being%20a%20politician%2C%20there%20was%20a%20rule%20in%20the%20house%20that%20no%20discussions%20over%20politics%20shall%20be%20held%20at%20the%20dinner%20table%2C%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20grandfather%20and%20I%20often%20dined%20together%20and%20he%20used%20to%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20nationalism%2C%20life%2C%20wisdom%2C%20and%20religion.%20Politics%20was%20never%20discussed%20at%20home.%20It%20was%20neither%20a%20part%20of%20our%20dinner%20nor%20breakfast%20table%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%2C%20however%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20aware%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20happenings%20in%20the%20country%20as%20it%20was%20mandatory%20to%20read%20a%20newspaper%20every%20morning%20before%20going%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dadu%20(grandfather)%20would%20sit%20with%20me%20with%20his%20tea%20and%20I%20sipped%20milk%20and%20together%20we%20used%20to%20go%20through%20newspapers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20wanted%20her%20to%20be%20in%20politics%2C%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20never%20talked%20about%20it.%20We%20only%20spoke%20about%20my%20career%20as%20a%20lawyer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20May%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Bansuri%20Swaraj%20said%20the%20hectic%20campaigning%20has%20left%20her%20%26quot%3Bsleep%20deprived%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20daily%20chats%20with%20her%20father%20and%20listening%20to%20music%20help%20her%20unwind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20days%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20I%20crave%20is%20sleep.%20I%20am%20quite%20sleep-deprived%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwaraj%20is%20one%20of%20the%20two%20women%20candidates%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20party%20is%20aiming%20to%20sweep%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20is%20fighting%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20as%20part%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20Congress.%20It%20has%20fielded%20Somnath%20Bharti%20from%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713008340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0kcgl9o_bansuri-swaraj-sushma-swaraj_625x3