rit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20back%20to%20where%20he%20belongs.%20After%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%2C%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20a%20crucial%20factor%20in%20the%20team's%20turnaround%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20after%20three%20straight%20losses.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20IPL%2C%20Bumrah's%20form%20will%20be%20crucial%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20too.%20Right%20after%20the%20IPL%202024%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20will%20play%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20After%20narrowly%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20title%20at%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20is%20once%20preparing%20to%20launch%20a%20goof%20fight%20for%20its%20first%20ICC%20title%20in%2013%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20are%20to%20do%20well%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20to%20play%20a%20big%20part%20in%20the%20bowling%20unit.%20Recently%2C%20Bumrah%20had%20a%20special%20chat%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiocinema.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fthe-bumrah-interview-with-sanjana-ganesan%2F3948065%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJio%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20renowned%20sports%20anchor%20Sanjana%20Ganesan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20asked%20you%20this%2C%20what%20have%20these%2010-11%20years%20been%20like%20(living%20in%20Mumbai)%3F%26quot%3B%20Sanjana%20Ganesan%20asked%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20very%20good%2C%20Came%20here%20as%20a%2019%20year%20old.%20That%20year%20didn't%20even%20expect%20to%20play%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20Yes%2C%20I%20was%20in%20the%20set%20up.%20But%20then%20John%20Wright%20saw%20me%20and%20brought%20me.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I%20have%20grown%20here.%20I%20have%20had%20an%20interesting%20journey.%20Won%20five%20titles.%20I%20have%20been%20part%20of%20all%20those%20winning%20squads.%20It's%2