king%20India%20up%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20BJP's%20strategy%20for%20the%20ensuing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20BJP's%20calculated%20strategy%20to%20paint%20the%20entire%20Opposition%20as%20anti-Hindu%20and%20to%20boost%20Narendra%20Modi's%20credentials%20as%20the%20saviour%20of%20Hindus.%20Hinduism%20is%20not%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20could%20be%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20ensuing%20election%2C%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUndoubtedly%2C%20she%20is%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20election.%20Her%20ability%20to%20hold%20the%20fort%20in%20West%20Bengal%20will%20strengthen%20the%20INDIA%20combination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20Kachchatheevu%20issue%20was%20%26quot%3Bclosed%26quot%3B%20and%20questioned%20the%20BJP's%20timing%20of%20raising%20the%20issue%20when%20the%20elections%20were%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKachchatheevu%20is%20a%20closed%20issue.%20The%20agreement%20was%20reached%2050%20years%20ago.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20been%20in%20office%20since%202014%3B%20why%20did%20he%20not%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kachchatheevu%20issue%20pertains%20to%20decades-old%20territorial%20and%20fishing%20rights%20dispute%20around%20the%20island%20located%20between%20Rameswaram%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20It%20gained%20prominence%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20as%20both%20BJP%20and%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20war%20of%20words%20over%20the%20issue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713003960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.nd