icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbjp-destroyed-ambedkars-constitution-says-mamata-tells-voters-dont-fall-prey-to-pm-modis-guarantees%2Farticleshow%2F109269232.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mexico%20Warns%20Of%20%26quot%3BZombie%20Drug%26quot%3B%20Xylazine%20Found%20In%20Opioids%20On%20US%20Border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20cities%20across%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Britain%2C%20the%20animal%20tranquillizer%20Xylazine%20has%20already%20been%20identified%20as%20a%20concerning%20threat.%20Now%2C%20Mexican%20public%20health%20officials%20are%20raising%20concerns%20after%20a%20study%20found%20xylazine%20present%20in%20opioids%20in%20cities%20along%20the%20country's%20northwest%20border%20with%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENicknamed%20%26quot%3Btranq%20dope%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bzombie%20drug%2C%26quot%3B%20Xylazine%20has%20worsened%20the%20opioid%20crisis%20in%20US%20cities%20like%20Philadelphia.%20It%20can%20make%20overdoses%20harder%20to%20treat%20and%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexico's%20health%20ministry%20issued%20an%20alert%20for%20medical%20personnel%20and%20first%20responders%20in%20border%20cities.%20Xylazine%20is%20not%20approved%20for%20human%20use%20in%20either%20Mexico%20or%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gob.mx%2Fcms%2Fuploads%2Fattachment%2Ffile%2F906959%2FSAT._Alerta_en_ciudades_fronterizas_por_uso_de_Xilacina.pdf%5C%22%3Ealert%20issued%20by%20Mexico's%20health%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20conjunction%20with%20the%20mental%20health%20and%20addiction%20commission%20on%20April%208%2C%20%26quot%3Bfor%20health%20personnel%20and%20first%20responders%20in%20Mexican%20border%20cities%20for%20possible%20adulteration%20of%20heroin%20and%20fentanyl%20with%20Xylazine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3Enews%20agency%20Reuters%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20study%20by%20Mexico's%20National%20Institute%20of%20Psychiatry%20found%20xylazine%20in%2035%25%20of%20heroin%20samples%20and%2026%25%20of%20fentanyl%20samples%20tested%20in%20Tijuana%20and%20Mexico.%20The%20ongoing%20study%20was%20not%20specifically%20looking%20for%20xylazine%2C%20highlighting%20its%20surprising%20prevalence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20come%20amid%20concerns%20about%20fentanyl%20use%20rising%20within%20Mexico.%20Fentanyl%20is%20a%20powerful%20synthetic%20opioid%20responsible%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20overdose%20deaths%20in%20the%20US%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20seeking%20to%20identify%20adulterants%20in%20drugs%20and%20was%20not%20specifically%20looking%20for%20xylazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20surprised%20to%20find%20Xylazine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Clara%20Fleiz%2C%20an%20investigator%20at%20Mexico's%20National%20Institute%20of%20Psychiatry%20and%20the%20study's%20lead%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713002280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fbls0cvoo_fleshrotting-zombie-drug-_625x300_29_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmexico-warns-of-zombie-drug-xylazine-found-in-opioids-on-us-border-5433129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20findings%20come%20amid%20concerns%20about%20fentanyl%20use%20rising%20within%20Mexico.%20Fentanyl%20is%20a%20powerful%20synthetic%20opioid%20responsible%20for%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20overdose%20deaths%20in%20the%20US%20each%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmexico-warns-of-zombie-drug-xylazine-found-in-opioids-on-us-border-5433129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmexico-warns-of-zombie-drug-xylazine-found-in-opioids-on-us-border-5433129%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww