0labelling%20diary-based%20or%20malt-based%20beverages%20as%20'health%20drinks'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20over%20the%20'unhealthy'%20nature%20of%20Bournvita%20first%20arose%20after%20a%20YouTuber%20in%20his%20video%20slammed%20the%20powder%20supplement%20and%20informed%20that%20it%20contained%20excessive%20sugar%2C%20cocoa%20solids%20and%20harmful%20colourants%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20hazards%20in%20children%2C%20including%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712998560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fvosvf83g_bournvita-_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-bournvita-from-health-drinks-category-centres-big-order-5432701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20to%20the%20e-commerce%20companies%2C%20directing%20them%20to%20remove%20all%20drinks%20and%20beverages%20including%20Bournvita%20from%20the%20category%20of%20'health%20drinks'%2C%20on%20their%20portal%20and%20platforms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-bournvita-from-health-drinks-category-centres-big-order-5432701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-bournvita-from-health-drinks-category-centres-big-order-5432701%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-bournvita-from-health-drinks-category-centres-big-order-5432701%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3A%20PM%20takes%20dig%20at%20oppn%20with%20'Noob%20in%20politics'%20jibe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712997879000%2C%22visual%22%3