%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBu%2C%20Mayank%20has%20missed%20the%20last%20two%20games%20for%20LSG%20due%20to%20a%20workload%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevang%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20Delhi's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20team%2C%20feels%20Mayank%2C%20a%20player%20who%20has%20followed%20from%20close%20quarters%2C%20hasn't%20ticked%20all%20boxes%20yet%20to%20become%20eligible%20for%20an%20India%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20feels%20that%20a%20player%20like%20Mayank%2C%20who%20is%20susceptible%20to%20injuries%2C%20needs%20to%20play%20more%20games%20to%20justify%20his%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20special%20talent.%20Somebody%20who%20clocks%20155%20kmph%20is%20definitely%20special.%20So%20obviously%2C%20with%20the%20impact%20that%20the%20body%20goes%20through%2C%20there%20will%20be%20injuries%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20that%20they%20can't%20be%20managed.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20a%20way%20of%20grooming%20him.%20He%20will%20have%20to%20play%20more%20matches%20and%20go%20through%20the%20rigours%2C%20and%20then%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20assessed%20as%20to%20how%20he%20is%20able%20to%20withstand%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20told%20Sports%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20has%20to%20tick%20all%20the%20boxes%20if%20he%20wants%20to%20play%20for%20India%20in%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup.%20He%20can%20be%20better%20accessed%20if%20he%20can%20play%20all%2012%20or%2014%20matches%20in%20the%20IPL.%20Selectors%20need%20to%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20parameters%2C%20and%20if%20he%20is%20able%20to%20tick%20most%20of%20those%20boxes%2C%20then%20he%20will%20merit%20a%20selection.%20Then%20again%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20in%20Mayank's%20court%2C%20and%20he%20has%20to%20prove%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20also%20suggested%20that%20Mayank%20had%20a%20surprise%20factor%20during%20his%20first%20two%20IPL%20games%2C%20but%20the%20opposition%20teams%20might%20work%20out%20a%20way%20to%20tackle%20him.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20the%20former%20India%20selector%20feels%20that%20the%2021-year-old%20will%20have%20to%20work%20more%20on%20his%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSelectors%20also%20need%20to%20check%20his%20temperament%20and%20how%20he%20bounces%20back%20after%20an%20off%20day.%20Consistency%20in%20fitness%20and%20temperament%20are%20the%20other%20aspects%20that%20selectors%20will%20look%20at.%20Initially%2C%20he%20had%20the%20surprise%20element%20working%20in%20his%20favour%2C%20but%20now%20batters%20and%20think%20tanks%20will%20try%20to%20work%20out%20how%20to%20face%20him.%20So%2C%20how%20he%20manages%20to%20overcome%20that%20hurdle%20will%20be%20key.%20So%20Yadav%20has%20to%20tick%20two%20more%20boxes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712997780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Frcoe6dc_mayank-yadav_625x300_30_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fneed-to-check-his-temperament-ex-bcci-selectors-big-statement-on-mayank-yadav-and-why-he-is-not-yet-ready-for-india-5432302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayank%20Yadav's%20performance%20has%20already%20earned%20him%20backing%20of%20several%20experts%20for%20a%20place%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20have%20you%20done...'%3A%20Priyanka%20slams%20BJP%20for%20blaming%20Cong%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712997773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109267391%2Cimgsize-43774.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-attacks-bjp-how-long-will-you-keep-blaming-congress-you-have-been-in-power-for-last-10-years%2Farticleshow%2F109267322.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20criticized%20the%