%E2%80%9CThe%20rooms%20do%20not%20have%20TV%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shalini%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20anybody%20would%20want%20to%20sit%20in%20their%20room%20watching%20TV%20when%20you%20can%20sit%20outdoors%20in%20the%20orchard%20and%20enjoy%20the%20views.%20There%20are%20flowers%2C%20butterflies%2C%20and%20fruit%20trees%20all%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20can%20also%20take%20hikes%20up%20the%20hills%20or%20serene%20walks%20along%20the%20river%20and%20to%20nearby%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20huge%20riverside%20area%20with%20a%20tiny%20%E2%80%98beach%E2%80%99.%20We%20also%20have%20hammocks%2C%20creating%20a%20very%20relaxed%20atmosphere.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20are%20books%20available%20for%20reading.%20In%20our%20lounge%20area%2C%20we%20have%20board%20games%20like%20Monopoly%20and%20Clue%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20sits%20right%20beside%20Beas%20River.%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-9-1712578274-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20sits%20right%20beside%20Beas%20River.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20place%20even%20has%20a%20natural%20spring%20on%20the%20property.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20the%20day%20when%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20you%20could%20simply%20open%20a%20tap%2C%20stick%20your%20face%20under%20it%2C%20and%20drink%20water%2C%20right%3F%20Here%2C%20you%20can%20do%20exactly%20that!%20The%20taps%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20natural%20spring%20water%20and%20you%20can%20drink%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20enjoying%20nature%2C%20guests%20can%20also%20indulge%20in%20the%20delicious%20meals%20that%20Shalini%20prepares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lots%20of%20edible%20weeds%20growing%20on%20the%20property.%20So%2C%20my%20favourite%20thing%20is%20to%20pick%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20what%20is%20growing%20in%20the%20garden.%20Locally%2C%20they%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20gram)%20and%20make%20little%20dried%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(vegetable%20nuggets)%20out%20of%20it%20for%20winter%2C%20because%20nothing%20grows%20here%20in%20the%20cold%20weather.%20So%2C%20they%20dry%20whatever%20they%20grow%20in%20summer%20or%20make%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20keep%20them.%20I%20love%20serving%20my%20guests%20these%20%3Cem%3Ebadis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20zucchini-based%20dishes%20because%20it%20grows%20here%20in%20abundance.%20We%20prepare%20it%20in%20various%20ways.%20There%20are%20also%20local%20dishes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20like%20a%20bao%20stuffed%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20also%20uses%20fiddlehead%20fern%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248547%2Fhomemade-pickles-athey-nallatha-hafez-rahman-akshay-raveendran-kerala-homemakers-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20pickles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20other%20produce%20like%20persimmon%20%3Cem%3Eachar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20plum%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20peach%20jam%2C%20and%20quince%20jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20homestay%20steeped%20in%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20is%20the%20one%20who%20handles%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejugaads%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(an%20innovative%20way%20of%20problem-solving)%20as%20Shalini%20puts%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitin%20informs%20that%20the%20homestay%20was%20made%20keeping%20in%20mind%20that%20it%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20nature%20around.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20implemented%20a%20lot%20of%20eco-friendly%20and%20sustainable%20practices%20right%20from%20the%20design%20of%20the%20place.%20We%20also%20wanted%20to%20minimise%20our%20energy%20requirements.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20started%20from%20the%20architecture%20and%20planning%20phase%2C%20where%20we%20utilised%20natural%20ways%20of%20heating%20and%20maximised%20sunlight%20exposure%20during%20winter%20while%20minimising%20it%20in%20summer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20offers%20delicious%20meals%20like%20siddu%2C%20badi%2C%20and%20homemade%20pickles.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-10-1-1712578444