tsmanship%20course%20at%20Singhbhum%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20he%20remained%20unaware%20of%20the%20brutality%20experienced%20by%20workers%20exposed%20to%20silica%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202002%20that%20he%20first%20read%20about%20the%20rising%20deaths%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20in%20the%20East%20Singhbhum%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202003%2C%20I%20closely%20observed%20some%20silicosis%20patients.%20Most%20of%20them%20had%20difficulty%20in%20breathing%2C%20and%20could%20not%20sleep%20easily%20because%20of%20it.%20One%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20daughters%20told%20us%20that%20she%20visited%20the%20site%20daily%20to%20give%20lunch%20to%20her%20father%2C%20but%20she%20always%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20recognise%20him%20as%20everyone%20would%20be%20covered%20in%20silica%20dust%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilicosis%20is%20an%20incurable%20lung%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20inhalation%20of%20dust%20containing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20crystals%20%3C%2Fa%3Efound%20commonly%20in%20quartzite%2C%20granite%2C%20basalt%2C%20sandstone%2C%20agate%2C%20slate%20marble%2C%20and%20building%20materials%20like%20fire%20bricks%20and%20tiles.%20This%20exposes%20workers%20in%20dust-generating%20sites%20like%20factories%2C%20mining%20and%20construction%20sites%20to%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20contracting%20the%20disease%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20prolonged%20illness%20and%20painful%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-3-1711118905.jpg%5C%22%2