C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346640%2Fbengaluru-water-scarcity-crisis-solutions-lake-revival-open-wells-rainwater-harvesting-treated-wastewater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPart%201%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20series%2C%20we%20discussed%20a%20variety%20of%20problems%20and%20solutions%20on%20a%20policy%20level%20about%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20current%20water%20crisis%2C%20addressing%20issues%20ranging%20from%20state%20failure%20to%20reviving%20lakes%2C%20recharging%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%2C%20building%20open%20recharge%20wells%2C%20and%20using%20treated%20wastewater%20as%20a%20genuine%20resource.%20Here%20we%E2%80%99ll%20discuss%20what%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20help!)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20issues%20of%20state%20capacity%20and%20the%20need%20to%20recalibrate%20water%20policy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20mitigate%20the%20water%20scarcity%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296593%2Fbengaluru-floods-zenrainman-s-vishwanath-expert-shares-water-logging-solutions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%20Vishwanath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20civil%20engineer%20and%20urban%20planner%20with%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20water%20and%20sanitation%20sector%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20consume%20less%20water%2C%20recycle%20greywater%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20to%20minimise%20my%20demand%2C%20then%20there%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20water%20which%20I%20can%20save%20within%20my%20whole%20zone.%20And%20the%20administration%20can%20transfer%20some%20of%20my%20zone%E2%80%99s%20water%20to%20another%20which%20is%20facing%20scarcity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20living%20in%20the%20affected%20area%2C%20especially%20in%20apartment%20complexes%20with%2020%20units%20or%20more%20(that%20are%20mandated%20to%20have%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%2C%20Vishwanath%20believes%20that%20if%20they%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants%20are%20running%20well%2C%20then%20they%20can%20fulfil%20all%20their%20non-potable%20water%20requirements%20from%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20residents%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20well%2C%20their%20borewells%20will%20have%20water.%20If%20the%20community%20works%20around%20the%20lakes%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20comes%20together%2C%20and%20makes%20sure%20that%20the%20lake%20is%20cleaned%20up%20and%20de-silted%20along%20with%20the%20State%2C%20then%20these%20water%20bodies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20their%20STPs%20that%20are%20well%20treated%20can%20be%20led%20into%20these%20lakes%20so%20that%20it%20recharges%20the%20aquifers.%20I%20believe%20these%20are%20all%20the%20steps%20that%20citizens%20have%20to%20take%20to%20protect%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20steps%20has%20he%20taken%20in%20his%20own%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20being%20mindful%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20you%20consume%2C%20you%20can%20deploy%20technologies%20like%20aerators%20on%20your%20taps%20or%20shower%20heads.%20You%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20water%20you%20collect%20after%20cleaning%20your%20dishes%20is%20used%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20or%20the%20garden%20that%20you%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20case%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20all%20the%20greywater%20is%20recycled.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20collect%20the%20wastewater%20from%20my%20washing%20machine%20and%20half-bucket%20bath%20water.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20n