-3-1712555430-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346770%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20as%20a%20commando%2C%20Mukesh%20had%20already%20started%20preparing%20himself%20to%20take%20up%20farming.%20But%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20after%20his%20father%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer.%20%E2%80%9CSix%20months%20later%2C%20my%20father%20lost%20his%20life%20to%20the%20disease.%20His%20last%20advice%20to%20me%20was%20to%20take%20up%20date%20farming%20for%20a%20profitable%20farming%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%203-day%20training%20programme%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20for%20Date%20Palm%20at%20Sagra-Bhojka%20in%20the%20Jaisalmer%20district.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20state%20government%20was%20promoting%20date%20cultivation%20in%20Rajasthan%20by%20distributing%20subsidised%20date%20palm%20saplings%20to%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20procured%20250%20date%20palm%20seeds%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342788%2Fyellow-dates-farming-in-india-engineer-quits-job-to-become-an-agripreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyellow-coloured%20Barhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20red-coloured%20Khuneji%20varieties%20and%20planted%20them%20on%20his%20farmland.%20It%20took%20four%20years%20before%20he%20saw%20the%20first%20fruit%20on%20the%20date%20palm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20grow%20money%20on%20trees%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20points%20out%20that%20growing%20dates%20have%20been%20extremely%20fruitful%20as%20both%20Barh